contents.shortDescription: A compact modern armchair that offers comfortable and sleek styling to accent your home's living room.
contents.longDescription: Give your living room a bold new look with the modern and comfortable blue armchair. The armchair features a compact design, comfortable oversized pillow, easy to clean polyester fabric, and button tufts along the lower backrest. The armchair's modern styling is complemented with durable light brown wooden legs. No assembly required.
